<h1 local-id=3D"d9dd61b0dda5" id=3D"T10-TechnicalDocument-Step4=E2=80=93Ins=
tallCloudWatchAgent">Step 4 =E2=80=93 Install CloudWatch Agent</h1>
<h3 local-id=3D"bbdbb136717b" id=3D"T10-TechnicalDocument-WhyCloudWatchAgen=
tWasInstalled">Why CloudWatch Agent Was Installed</h3>
<p local-id=3D"40e6d839f170">By default, EC2 sends only basic metrics to Cl=
oudWatch such as:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"ec4f479384a7">CPU utilization</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"0b9be6ec7756">Network traffic</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"e7ecff50f5e4">Disk I/O</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"b33f6cc5075a">However, <strong>memory usage and disk utiliza=
tion are not available by default</strong>.</p>
<p local-id=3D"a0de79e90c65">To collect these additional system metrics, th=
e <strong>CloudWatch Agent</strong> was installed on each instance.</p>
<p local-id=3D"93afabc5032a">Installation command:</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">sudo yu=
m install amazon-cloudwatch-agent -y</pre>
</div>
</div>
<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"853b58551a9f" id=3D"T10-TechnicalDocument-Step5=E2=80=93Con=
figureCloudWatchAgent">Step 5 =E2=80=93 Configure CloudWatch Agent</h1>
<p local-id=3D"9cb4149fcc3a">The CloudWatch Agent was configured using:</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">amazon-=
cloudwatch-agent.json</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"cb950857338d">The configuration collects the following metri=
cs.</p>
<p local-id=3D"92efb7aea04a"><strong>Memory metrics</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"66638fe2054f">mem_used_percent</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"8605f744caf3">mem_available</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"151060c3f7be">mem_total</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"d21502a02dce"><strong>Disk metrics</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"cbc417ac160d">disk_used_percent</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"b36eff303e34">disk_free</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"4b8d1242dd26">disk_total</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"00c2f28bc95b">These metrics are published under the <strong>=
CWAgent namespace</strong>.</p>
<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"c37a583b32ac" id=3D"T10-TechnicalDocument-Step6=E2=80=93Sta=
rtCloudWatchAgent">Step 6 =E2=80=93 Start CloudWatch Agent</h1>
<p local-id=3D"75de636cc492">The agent was started using:</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">sudo sy=
stemctl start amazon-cloudwatch-agent</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"12fbaede7f04">Agent status was verified using:</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">sudo sy=
stemctl status amazon-cloudwatch-agent</pre>
</div>
</div><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper =
confluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image im=
age-center" alt=3D"Screenshot 2026-03-06 162046-20260306-105047.png" width=
=3D"468" loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"c2a351c8a98ab9ea8bebfe19b69cc82e29c2ff62c7=
6f844d052026e08a165aa0" data-image-src=3D"https://iamops.atlassian.net/wiki=
/download/attachments/1837039669/Screenshot%202026-03-06%20162046-20260306-=
105047.png?version=3D3&amp;modificationDate=3D1772868571326&amp;cacheVersio=
n=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" data-height=3D"296" data-width=3D"1439" data-unresolved=
-comment-count=3D"0" data-linked-resource-id=3D"1841397796" data-linked-res=
ource-version=3D"3" data-linked-resource-type=3D"attachment" data-linked-re=
