<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"74da6c927b6c" id=3D"T10-TechnicalDocument-Step7=E2=80=93Cre=
ateCloudWatchDashboard">Step 7 =E2=80=93 Create CloudWatch Dashboard</h1>
<p local-id=3D"d36c0aeea95d">A custom dashboard named:</p>
<p local-id=3D"ba63426bd9f0"><strong>EC2-Infrastructure-Monitoring</strong>=
</p>
<p local-id=3D"315068becdbe">was created in CloudWatch.</p>
<p local-id=3D"ad1ce0109651">The dashboard design focuses on:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"ebabdd730195">compact layout</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"185f4745bf8d">easy readability</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"dccb1696ee54">quick system understanding</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"5b5bbe085c06">The design follows the <strong>5-second rule</=
strong>.</p>
<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"20534b80970b" id=3D"T10-TechnicalDocument-Step8=E2=80=93Add=
MonitoringWidgets">Step 8 =E2=80=93 Add Monitoring Widgets</h1>
<p local-id=3D"02c615bc5f7f">The following widgets were added to the dashbo=
ard.</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"1800" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"c=
30dcb04-2a06-4750-9e41-7c773d39a5b6" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
