<p local-id=3D"7e4e1f857bda">Disk Usage</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"e32adcf48200">Area Chart</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"d75e6c668b41">Memory Usage</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"02a2203a4b7a">Gauge</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"d2c0a61da773">These visualizations allow quick comparison of=
 infrastructure performance across instances.</p><span class=3D"confluence-=
