<h1 local-id=3D"93e2095c7974" id=3D"T10-TechnicalDocument-6.MonitoringandIn=
cidentManagement">6. Monitoring and Incident Management</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"9a5d4b3c8670" id=3D"T10-TechnicalDocument-6.1MonitoringTool=
sandMetrics">6.1 Monitoring Tools and Metrics</h2>
<p local-id=3D"3bd17996af05">Monitoring is implemented using Amazon CloudWa=
tch.</p>
<p local-id=3D"f9351cf9946a">Metrics monitored include:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"d70f8c9a561f">CPU utilization</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"9c4da3a72a93">Memory usage</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"d007775f02a6">Disk usage</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"8d5b482078f2">Network traffic</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"1c9259c0e476">These metrics provide real-time infrastructure=
 insights.</p>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"c8b85de3db2f" id=3D"T10-TechnicalDocument-6.2AlertingandNot=
ification">6.2 Alerting and Notification</h2>
<p local-id=3D"8ed6c0c95fab">CloudWatch alarms can be configured to notify =
teams when metric thresholds are exceeded.</p>
<p local-id=3D"3d4372e08d07">Alerts can be integrated with email or messagi=
ng services.</p>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"e55e50588620" id=3D"T10-TechnicalDocument-6.3IncidentManage=
ment">6.3 Incident Management</h2>
<p local-id=3D"6ee5a0df79d1">When abnormal behavior is detected:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p local-id=3D"597d17589ebc">Identify the affected instance</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"5a2ef2583e3d">Review system metrics</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"9e7fa5d583c1">Analyze logs</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"960bda1d39ee">Apply corrective actions</p></li>
</ol>
<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"b909c6e2ba79" id=3D"T10-TechnicalDocument-7.Security&amp;Co=
mpliance">7. Security &amp; Compliance</h1>
<p local-id=3D"242b07071918">Security practices implemented include:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"ce39ad9aac35">IAM roles for monitoring permissions</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"555bc464d623">controlled access to CloudWatch resources</p><=
/li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"8168deb7a854">secure EC2 access configuration</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"2508f81fb9b9" id=3D"T10-TechnicalDocument-8.CostOptimisatio=
n">8. Cost Optimisation</h1>
<p local-id=3D"42231b036058">Cost optimization strategies included:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"d1883491d72e">using lightweight EC2 instances</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"dc410182a58f">minimizing infrastructure resources</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"0f165732f48b">efficient monitoring architecture</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
