<p local-id=3D"f24cbe0fe605">Final delivery includes dashboard and document=
ation.</p>
<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"d5eb6515ffb5" id=3D"T10-TechnicalDocument-11.ContinuousImpr=
ovement">11. Continuous Improvement</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"70cb94b649f4" id=3D"T10-TechnicalDocument-11.1FeedbackandRe=
trospectives">11.1 Feedback and Retrospectives</h2>
<p local-id=3D"ba77c11aff3e">Feedback from DevOps teams can improve dashboa=
rd design and monitoring coverage.</p>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"0f703cfe1bc4" id=3D"T10-TechnicalDocument-11.2IterativeEnha=
ncements">11.2 Iterative Enhancements</h2>
<p local-id=3D"0bc29eb9e00d">Future improvements may include:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"5716589ec340">automated alerts</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"a579487121b6">log monitoring</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"407010735750">auto-scaling integration</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"02914cf4b8e1">advanced analytics</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"3b9a51f49ddf" id=3D"T10-TechnicalDocument-12.Conclusion">12=
. Conclusion</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"35f1d0bcdd17" id=3D"T10-TechnicalDocument-12.1Summary">12.1=
 Summary</h2>
<p local-id=3D"3fbd931c9381">This project implemented centralized infrastru=
cture monitoring using Amazon CloudWatch.</p>
<p local-id=3D"a412c582076f">By integrating EC2 instances, enabling detaile=
d monitoring, installing the CloudWatch agent, and designing a compact dash=
board, the solution provides clear visibility into infrastructure performan=
ce.</p>
<p local-id=3D"59f38667e490">The dashboard follows the <strong>5-second rul=
e</strong>, enabling quick understanding of system health.</p>
<hr>
<h2 local-id=3D"d9dfd245e856" id=3D"T10-TechnicalDocument-12.2NextSteps">12=
.2 Next Steps</h2>
<p local-id=3D"35ccd0122a72">Future improvements may include:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"adc5ac8dc848">automated alerting</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"d3765d7c7e2e">CI/CD integration</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"034ff6b22d15">enhanced monitoring metrics</p></li>
